  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT ALWAYS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ALWAYS: ILL is a psychological horror experience that plunges you into a world where memories lie, shadows breathe, and every step draws you deeper into a reality you can no longer trust. You play as a man shattered by loss, desperately searching for his missing daughter in the aftermath of a mysterious catastrophe. As you explore abandoned towns, decaying homes, and twisted dreamscapes, the line between the living and the dead begins to blur.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What begins as a search turns into a descent—into madness, into grief, into a hidden world governed by a dark ritual and a forbidden pact. Something ancient is watching. Something that feeds on pain… and wants you to remember.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate eerie environments, solve emotional and environmental puzzles, and survive chilling encounters in a game that fuses cinematic storytelling with terrifying gameplay. But be warned: in ALWAYS, it's not just what’s in front of you that you should fear—it’s what’s been buried deep within.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652040/extras/8596f9d572d63004ca9d561aba6030e8.poster.avif?t=1748390199\" width=800 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652040/extras/8596f9d572d63004ca9d561aba6030e8.webm?t=1748390199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652040/extras/8596f9d572d63004ca9d561aba6030e8.mp4?t=1748390199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652040/extras/a8d016b32e2f4b96d62edb32cb6922db.avif?t=1748390199\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652040/extras_big/a8d016b32e2f4b96d62edb32cb6922db.avif?t=1748390199 width=800 height=50 /></span>ALWAYS: ILL GAME LORE</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After losing his daughter, a broken detective clings to the sound of her voice — until an accident pulls him into a twisted nightmare. Trapped in haunting echoes of her past, he must solve puzzles and uncover chilling clues to stop a deranged man from sacrificing his child... to bring back his own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652040/extras/32eb1819a02b8f24e8d933c40b090394.poster.avif?t=1748390199\" width=800 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652040/extras/32eb1819a02b8f24e8d933c40b090394.webm?t=1748390199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652040/extras/32eb1819a02b8f24e8d933c40b090394.mp4?t=1748390199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652040/extras/a8d016b32e2f4b96d62edb32cb6922db.avif?t=1748390199\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652040/extras_big/a8d016b32e2f4b96d62edb32cb6922db.avif?t=1748390199 width=800 height=50 /></span>ALWAYS: ILL GAME FEATURES</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique, Smart Puzzles</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve a variety of logic-based and environmental puzzles that challenge your perception.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Psychological Horror Atmosphere</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a disturbing world where reality shifts constantly and every location tells a piece of a deeper, darker truth.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cinematic Storytelling</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a haunting narrative focused on a father’s emotional journey to find his daughter, with professionally crafted cutscenes and in-game storytelling moments.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First-Person Immersion</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore detailed, atmospheric environments from a first-person perspective that enhances tension, discovery, and dread.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quick-Time Survival Events (QTEs)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in intense, heart-pounding moments where quick reflexes are the difference between life and death.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Emotion-Driven Exploration</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every location, item, and puzzle is tied to the character’s emotional past, making exploration meaningful and impactful.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic Sound Design</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Designed to keep you on edge, with subtle audio cues, whispers, footsteps, and unsettling ambiance following your every move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652040/extras/57c53be45f440b202b5c7a3908470a66.poster.avif?t=1748390199\" width=800 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652040/extras/57c53be45f440b202b5c7a3908470a66.webm?t=1748390199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3652040/extras/57c53be45f440b202b5c7a3908470a66.mp4?t=1748390199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
